section.section:
"Insurer" means:
a stock corporation or mutual association that is authorized under the Insurance Article to provide workers' compensation insurance in the State;
a governmental self-insurance group that meets the requirements of § 9-404 of this title;
a self-insurance group of private employers that meets the requirements of Title 25, Subtitle 3 of the Insurance Article; or
an individual employer that self-insures in accordance with § 9-405 of this title.
